channel.description:
After shuting down my old server, for a few months i wanted to create pk server. I am using the same source as i did on old deathslay.
If the websites on the pictures is against rules tell me. no one gos on it any more, we have new fourm.
[img]http://oi56.tinypic.com/j5un14.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1201.photobucket.com/albums/bb351/Deathslay/deathslaybanner.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1201.photobucket.com/albums/bb351/Deathslay/deathslayoldbanner.jpg[/img]
Right now i have currently done:
-removed un needed commands -cleaned out client.java -made shops -got rid of alot of lagg in source -stuff that i did when reg source was open dont remember :\
Stuff im going to do: -pk point shop -shops sell armor and food (cheap) -might make spawn server -more stuff just dont know yet
looking for coder. and beta testers. i will also be looking for mods and admins later. just need to get the server up and running with things tested.
You have any questions please contact me on msn: deathslay317@hotmail.com
here are pictures of my old server. the new deathslay pvp has all that but im cleaning/deleting alot of stuff thats not needed for pvp [img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/17098176/bloodisdone.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i1201.photobucket.com/albums/bb351/Deathslay/0044.png[/img]

yes this is delta but its not noticeable.
